snippet.title: J-Jump Arena - Gameplay Reveal Teaser
snippet.description:
A turn based, jumping elimination game where every player moves simulatenously! Learn to be precise with your jumps and weapon handling, as well as in the art of outsmarting your opponents! Multiplayer for up to 10 players and single player mode available.

Link to Steam Store page:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1949970/JJump_Arena/
